  "Our Story": "我们的故事",
  "Since February 2021, at": "自2021年2月起，在",
  "we have been working for animal welfare.": "我们一直致力于动物福利。",
  "We are a Costa Rican family business that was born out of a genuine need and the creative vision of a couple who saw a problem and committed themselves to creating new possibilities.": "我们是一家哥斯达黎加家族企业，源于真实的需求和一对夫妇的创意愿景，他们看到了问题并致力于创造新的可能性。",
  "The Problem that Moved Us": "感动我们的问题",
  "We have had to live through the experience of losing our pets, as well as seeing loved ones suffer from the same situation. We feel that inexplicable mix of emotions: anguish, uncertainty, despair.": "我们不得不经历失去宠物的痛苦，也看到亲人遭受同样的处境。我们感受到那种难以言喻的情感混合：痛苦、不确定、绝望。",
  "We could not accept that in 2021, pet identification continued to be scarce, tedious, and subject to expiration dates, leaving our companions vulnerable. life.": "我们无法接受在2021年，宠物识别仍然稀缺、繁琐且受限于有效期，使我们的同伴处于脆弱状态。",
  "The Solution We Believe In": "我们相信的解决方案",
  "We clearly saw that more comprehensive, up-to-date, and permanent pet identification was not only possible but absolutely necessary. With technology as our ally, we could provide a real and effective solution.": "我们清楚地看到，更全面、最新且永久性的宠物识别不仅可能，而且绝对必要。借助技术作为我们的盟友，我们可以提供真正有效的解决方案。",
  "This is how our commitment was born: to revolutionize the way we protect our pets, making their safety accessible, modern, and permanent.": "这就是我们承诺的诞生：彻底改变我们保护宠物的方式，使它们的安全易于获取、现代化且永久。",
  "Our Journey": "我们的旅程",
  "The Beginning": "开始",
  "We began to assemble the small but mighty team that, to this day, remains the heart of our company. We dedicated months of intense work, research, and development to launch": "我们开始组建小而强大的团队，至今仍是公司的核心。我们投入了数月的紧张工作、研究和开发，以推出",
  "with our first product: the": "我们的第一个产品：",
  "Smart Tags": "智能标签",
  "Growth": "成长",
  "Thanks to the beautiful community that trusted us from the very beginning, we have been able to grow and expand our services. Today, we are proud to offer a complete app that goes beyond pet identification, providing comprehensive care solutions.": "感谢从一开始就信任我们的美丽社区，我们得以成长并扩展服务。今天，我们自豪地提供一个超越宠物识别的完整应用，提供全面的护理解决方案。",
  "Our Core Values": "我们的核心价值观",
  "Our Milestones": "我们的里程碑",
  "The Future We Build Together": "我们共同建设的未来",
  "We have many challenges ahead of us and we are eager to overcome them. We continue to innovate, grow, and improve in order to offer you the best solutions for the well-being of your pets.": "我们面前有许多挑战，我们渴望克服它们。我们不断创新、成长和改进，为您宠物的福祉提供最佳解决方案。",
  "Will you join us on this journey?": "您会加入我们这段旅程吗？",
